{
    "name": "Ogre Destroyer",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Ogre",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<i>This lumbering giant\u2019s beady eyes are devoid of wit or kindness, and its puffy face features a wide mouth with ill-fitting teeth.</i>"
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "An ogre destroyer is profane, disgusting, and filled with rage; nothing is safe from his murderous and hateful urges. He indulges every whim, revels in the powers granted by his dark patrons, and lives utterly free of all civilized restraint. He represents what people think of when they hear the word \u201cantipaladin.\u201d"
        }
    ],
